{"tid":1491879,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合] 你要知道的急救知識","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:17:14.000Z","uid":142276,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eb8ec31b500d50cc61609b875e964782338fa7b5","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"整合左少少資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其入元朗呢啲高危地方，大家最好防範未然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5yotvi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5yotvi.png&h=3d60107c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAmEMgY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwAmEMgY.png&h=cf57bdb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANOf33F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANOf33F.png&h=32e24de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n---<br />\n【重要】斬人風氣下必須急救知識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1490171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1490171</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5864ec8db329d691bad63904dbf7e9bb72348da2","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八月二十日1點57分，景林去厚德連儂隧道有一男一女被人持菜刀斬。當時佢地只係痴緊sticker，就俾個人攞菜刀砍，其中一人中頸！<br />\n<br />\n所有手足都要同我學識點保護自己，點做刀傷既急救，對抗白色恐怖！唔好奉旨身邊一定會有FA啊！</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，要守望相助！<br />\n香港人，加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"da2835f16987c298f10997c10be30764212815bb","tid":1491879,"uid":159405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"Pishh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba897a1b39f309ac64e3293dc31c87a7b63e855","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b486d0542847760a55cfec91e47737a79045ccd","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>俾人打到牙齒鬆脫/咬斷舌頭應該點幫手</blockquote>最緊要確保氣管係暢通冇塞住 <br />\n要吐番甩左既牙or脷出黎 <br />\n如果跌左入氣管會抖啱到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>拍背隻幫傷者吐翻異物出黎力度有無咩要求 我驚好似電視劇咁拍到噴血<br />\n牙齒我知要放入冰牛奶帶去醫院<br />\n咁其他身體部位呢？如果好恐怖斷手腳有無辦法盡量延長駁得翻嘅機會？<br />\n唉點解香港會變成咁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFPromb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFPromb.png&h=a75d9e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle左張圖 清晰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有異物 清醒的話會鼓勵佢儘量自己咳出黎先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"18436e52fc0592e9a4bf83d81a30190fb5fd0014","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當係好急去處理手腳大量出血<br />\n如果按壓都唔得既話<br />\n就可以用一條粗少少帶去扎住傷口對上既位置<br />\n確實位置一個普通人未必識<br />\n但係扎住先既話的確可以減少動/靜脈流血<br />\n<br />\n但一定要記住, 唔可以扎太耐<br />\n純粹真係無資源同埋無救護車到之前既辦法<br />\n太耐既話會組織壞死</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e63fa521e255c236a097af3d6a79fd31d8823fe","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"一齊學急救知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a14f9c44c97aa861a24b9048d6c2bc81257bb12","tid":1491879,"uid":155033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c095f2b4a23e8004d29535f46d42017547f9797","tid":1491879,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"要俾多d人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43c847f1bc2bf9f6ac04918b0360549fcb225ee","tid":1491879,"uid":152522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22d29703f877966ab9d8eb51e03dffadf4af8cf","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:24:29.000Z","msg":"如果冇乾淨布 可以用m巾頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99c8e36f973277f1a6e60c9af56512070c663f4","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真 到時見到人拎刀驚到仆街係正常<br />\n所以最好係走 除非你好好好有信心還拖成功<br />\n記得叫救命 大叫有刀手斬人 起碼會有人幫拖<br />\n有咩事保住個頭同頸</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d75005383988422ada470a1227160790abdfa175","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人睇到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300b44e51cb617a3e4aaa634242fe3604f004693","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰3個唔係去遊行 而係喺屋企樓下都比人斬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以基本上每個人會出街都應該學甚本急救知識 唔洗話一定join急救班 無時間上網自學當增值自己都得<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=0thq3rPA8cU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0thq3rPA8cU&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9mdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=d602c6fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=0thq3rPA8cU</a><br />\n\t</blockquote><br />\nP.S.如果冇First Aid牌唔可以叫自己做急救員，但學定啲基本急救知識防身都要掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49e33f92069499369138101bd5f1a3d7ae99c90","tid":1491879,"uid":3705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"803bf30eccd77aa5d409a98ea2ad26f8c7ffdcdb","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"一齊學急救知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶定First Aid物資旁身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03274cc4406b1e30607d68a7dd77a66e8761c952","tid":1491879,"uid":283344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2fc37a8d079cd559c06a8536064d19c0e655fbce","tid":1491879,"uid":283344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03274cc4406b1e30607d68a7dd77a66e8761c952","tid":1491879,"uid":283344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"6baf274bff8464d01e42f617b4e0c3ae6f3fbe5b","tid":1491879,"uid":138331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"必須正評"},{"pid":"fd34ccad2cf4f18ffba2ab1a65815dc64174b13b","tid":1491879,"uid":138331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安"},{"pid":"35f8a0841587d660fe62af343dff5e064a75398a","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:10:41.000Z","msg":"推比多啲人睇到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38053954655491ddbc328040c1d7f374bb587cb6","tid":1491879,"uid":142276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊學急救知識<img src=\